729912f-b.title: Richmond: Willowbrook Road - Collfield Avenue
729912f-b.text:
(A)
849 Willowbrook Road, north side, between Collfield and
Decatur Avenues, showing the Tom Barnes House (so referred to
by Mr. Sperr).
November 2,1922
By Wa. T. Davis through P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, at a later date.
1924
P. L. Sperr

729913f-a.title: Richmond: Willowbrook Road - Collfield Avenue
729913f-a.text:
(1)
B67 Willowbrook Road, north side, west of Collfield
Avenue. The house was owned by T. Standering in 1874 and by
Cutter from 1898 to 1907 (see maps of above dates). On the
extreme left is visible the old Tom Barnes house.
May 6, 1929
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, at a later date.
May 21, 1932
P. L. Sperr
